      <p>This paper analyzes all 12 scheduled bouts for UFC Fight Night: Sterling vs. Zalal using a structured quantitative framework. Fighter profiles, recent form, stylistic matchup analysis, and current market odds were synthesized to produce an independent probability assessment for each fight. Where my implied probabilities diverge meaningfully from market odds, potential value asymmetries are flagged.</p>

