            The wrestling-vs-BJJ dynamic. Sterling's top control and takedowns vs. Zalal's submission game from bottom. If Sterling can control position without getting submitted, he likely wins on volume. If Zalal can scramble to dominant positions or land a submission from the guard, he wins. Sterling's 5-round cardio edge could matter late.
